Class Bucket

java.lang.Object
  objects.Bucket

public class Bucket
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
Soroush this is the bucket object. each bucket has an array-list of nodes, indexes and coverings in it. capacity is number of prefixes that can be added to this bucket. each index, covering and node in this object is a string containing '1', '0' and '*' and the end of it.
